As he walked in the dome he would fight in, Daemos opened a frequency he 
hoped would be the one to the IGL staff.

Daemos:
To the IGL staff, this is Daemos of the Tripredacus. I am sorry of having 
been too hasty to wait for some escort to my dome. I would like to be 
informed as soon as my opponent arrives. Thank you.

He took one of his spike knives and heated it with his flaming hands to get 
himself out of boredom.
